Name: ImGui Widgets
Identifier: SDL
Depends:
	Build-Platforms: Windows, MacOSX, Linux, FreeBSD, DragonFlyBSD, OpenBSD
Description: Highly-customize-able and theme-able, custom-drawn, Dear ImGui Widgets powered by SDL Windowing, and SDL Renderer's OpenGL backend. Complete with custom localization and fonts support, using environment variables. On macOS, this is not compatible with the xlib platform and should be used with SDL.
Author: Samuel Venable
